

<div class="column gap-2">
  <div class="widget widget--single">
    Invest 
    <div class="ticker-input ticker-input--autoscale">
      <input type="text" class="numeric-input iu-numeric iu-autowidth" size="1" placeholder="0">
      <div class="ticker" style="background: #26A17B">USDT</div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="widget widget--single">
    <div class="widget-form">
      <div class="db-form__row db-form__row--input">
        <input class="db-form__input" type="text" value="" name="Public key" id="publicKey">
        <label class="db-form__label">Public key</label>
      </div>
      <div class="db-form__row db-form__row--input">
        <input class="db-form__input" type="text" value="" name="Private key" id="privateKey">
        <label class="db-form__label">Private key</label>
      </div>
      <div class="form-group db-form-group--main-btn">
        <input type="submit" name="commit" value="Connect" class="btn btn-lg btn-primary" data-disable-with="Connect">
      </div>
    </div>
    <ol>
      <li>Log into your <a href="https://www.probit.com/" target="_blank" rel="nofollow">ProBit Global</a> account.</li>
      <li>In the <b>My Page</b> menu (top right corner) go to <b>API Management</b>.</li>
      <li>Provide API key label and press <b>Create new key</b>.</li>
      <li>Confirm creation of API keys.</li>
      <li>If you want to restrict the access so only Deltabadger can use the keys, press <b>Edit</b> and set <b>IP Address Restriction</b> to this IP: <b>3.18.70.231</b></li>
      <li>
        Set permissions for: 
        <ul>
          <li><b>Read</b> </li>
          <li><b>Trading</b> </li>
        </ul>
      </li>
      <li>Copy and paste your new Client ID and Client's Secret Key into the form above.</li>
    </ol>
  </div>
  <div class="widget widget--single">
    <form data-controller="form--submit" action="" accept-charset="UTF-8" method="post"><input type="hidden" name="_method" value="patch">
    <div class="toggle">
      <input name="" disabled="disabled" type="hidden" value="0"><input data-action="change->form--submit#submit" disabled="disabled" type="checkbox" value="1" name="" id="portfolio_smart_allocation_on">
      <div class="toggle__style"></div>
      <label class="label" for="portfolio_smart_allocation_on">Market Cap adjusted</label>
      <div class="tooltip-info-icon" data-controller="tooltip" data-action="click->tooltip#toggle">
        <div class="tooltip-icon--off">
          <svg class="icon-24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
